import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import './index.css'; // Global styles
import App from './App'; // Optional: Import if you have a main App component
import MainPage from './MainPage'; // Import MainPage component
import SurveillanceForm from './surveillanceform'; // Import SurveillanceForm component
import SurgeonPage from './SurgeonPage'; // Import SurgeonPage component
import SeniorDoctorPage from './SeniorDoctorPage'; // Import SeniorDoctorPage component

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));

root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Router>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<MainPage />} />
        <Route path="/nurse" element={<SurveillanceForm />} />
        <Route path="/surgeon" element={<SurgeonPage />} />
        <Route path="/senior-doctor" element={<SeniorDoctorPage />} />
      </Routes>
    </Router>
  </React.StrictMode>
);
